        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-style:italic;font-size:1.05rem;color:#1c1917;margin:0 0 0.75rem;">Hawthorne properties sell quickly and a share never reach the portals. Registered buyers get first access.</p>
        <a href="/buyers" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;padding:0.85rem 1.6rem;background:#c4912a;color:#fff;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;">Register your buying criteria &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</article>

